1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
What if I told you your actions are being shaped without you knowing?

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:10,000
This is operant conditioning, where actions followed by rewards become more likely.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:16,800
Think about it—every time you get a compliment or a treat, you’re encouraged to repeat that behavior.

4
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:22,400
Studies show this can apply to everything from training pets to improving workplace performance.

5
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:25,200
Understanding this can help you change habits.

6
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,800
Want to learn how?

7
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:32,800
Hit follow for more insights into psychology and how to harness the power of rewards!
